Patch 6.2.079
Problem:    ":w ++enc=utf-8 !cmd" doesn't work.
Solution:   Check for the "++" argument before the "!".
Files:	    src/ex_docmd.c


*** ../vim-6.2.078/src/ex_docmd.c	Sun Aug 10 22:24:37 2003
--- src/ex_docmd.c	Sun Sep  7 14:26:29 2003
